window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>A war of magic. A legend of three elves. A new darkness on the horizon. </b></p> <p>I'm on the hunt for the enemy, but everything changes when the Official gets involved. </p> <p>After working with the three elves to bring Cyron's plans to a halt, the city is rebuilding and elves and humans are coexisting again.</p> <p>But clouds loom on the horizon as the Emperor makes noise that he will be returning from his meditation to manage his Empire. </p> <p>With the Official and now Emperor involved, the situation is bound to be interesting. Even more so with betrayal, magic, and lovemaking all thrown into the mix.</p> <p><b>Warning: </b>Contains mature harem content.</p>"; 
